Description: Smart area screenshot and clipboard history manager
 ClipSnap is an advanced screenshot and clipboard management tool for Linux
 desktop environments. It provides:
 .
  * Precision area screenshot capture with modern UI
  * Comprehensive clipboard history management
  * Global keyboard shortcuts for quick access
  * Automatic startup and system integration
  * SQLite-based history storage with thumbnails
  * Cross-desktop environment compatibility
 .
 ClipSnap integrates seamlessly with GNOME, KDE, XFCE, and other desktop
 environments, providing a professional screenshot and clipboard experience.